OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FA vast area of the Antarctic Ice Sheet
OL,7,F` Thwaites Glacier ` continues to
OL,8,Fretreat and much of it could be lost
OL,9,Fby the 23rd century, experts say.
OL,11,FThe glacier spans an area equal to the
OL,12,Fisland of Great Britain or the US
OL,13,Fstate of Florida, and in some places
OL,14,Fis more than 2,000 metres thick.
OL,16,FThe volume of ice flowing into the sea
OL,17,Ffrom Thwaites Glacier and its
OL,18,Fneighbouring glaciers has more than
OL,19,Fdoubled from the 1990s to the 2010s.
