OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FExperts say immediate and sustained
OL,7,Fclimate intervention is needed to make
OL,8,Fa positive difference.
OL,10,FSince 2018, researchers have uncovered
OL,11,Fa complex, rapidly changing
OL,12,Fenvironment at the remote glacier, and
OL,13,Fscientists from the UK and US are
OL,14,Fmeeting at British Antarctic Survey
OL,15,F(BAS) in Cambridge this week to
OL,16,Fdiscuss their observations.
