OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FBefore the start of the project, named
OL,7,Fthe International Thwaites Glacier
OL,8,FCollaboration (ITGC), little was known
OL,9,Fabout the mechanisms controlling the
OL,10,Fretreat of the huge glacier.
OL,12,FDr Rob Larter, from the Science Co-
OL,13,Fordination of the ITGC and a marine
OL,14,Fgeophysicist at BAS, said: "Thwaites
OL,15,Fhas been retreating for more than 80
OL,16,Fyears, accelerating considerably over
OL,17,Fthe past 30 years, and our findings
OL,18,Findicate it is set to retreat further
OL,19,Fand faster.
