OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,F"There is a consensus that Thwaites
OL,7,FGlacier retreat will accelerate
OL,8,Fsometime within the next century.
OL,10,F"However, there is also concern that
OL,11,Fadditional processes revealed by
OL,12,Frecent studies, which are not yet well
OL,13,Fenough studied to be incorporated into
OL,14,Flarge-scale models, could cause
OL,15,Fretreat to accelerate sooner."
OL,17,FThe latest findings suggest Thwaites
OL,18,FGlacier and much of the West Antarctic
OL,19,FIce Sheet could be lost by the 23rd
OL,20,Fcentury.
