OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FIts ice rests on a bed far below sea
OL,7,Flevel that slopes downwards towards
OL,8,Fthe heart of West Antarctica, making
OL,9,FThwaites Glacier particularly
OL,10,Fvulnerable.
OL,12,FResearchers have used underwater
OL,13,Frobots, new survey techniques, and new
OL,14,Fapproaches to ice flow and fracture
OL,15,Fmodelling, to gain new insights into
OL,16,Fthese processes.
