OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FThey say that although this has
OL,7,Fimproved the ability of computer
OL,8,Fmodels to predict what might happen,
OL,9,Fthere is still a lot that is not known
OL,10,Fabout the glacier's future.
OL,12,FAt roughly 120km across, Thwaites is
OL,13,Fthe widest glacier on the planet and
OL,14,Fis a keystone of the West Antarctic
OL,15,FIce Sheet, much of which sits on a bed
OL,16,Fbelow sea level and would raise sea
OL,17,Flevels by 3.3 metres if it all melted.
