OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FDr Ted Scambos, US science co-
OL,7,Fordinator of the ITGC and glaciologist
OL,8,Fat the University of Colorado, said:
OL,9,F"It's concerning that the latest
OL,10,Fcomputer models predict continuing ice
OL,11,Floss that will accelerate through the
OL,12,F22nd century and could lead to a
OL,13,Fwidespread collapse of the West
OL,14,FAntarctic Ice Sheet in the 23rd."
OL,16,FHe continued: "Immediate and sustained
OL,17,Fclimate intervention will have a
OL,18,Fpositive effect, but a delayed one,
OL,19,Fparticularly in moderating the
OL,20,Fdelivery of warm deep ocean water that
OL,21,Fis the main driver of retreat."
