OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FSo far, results from the studies
OL,7,Findicate that the rate of ice loss
OL,8,Ffrom the retreating glacier will
OL,9,Fincrease in response to climate and
OL,10,Focean changes.
OL,12,FAmong several potential scenarios for
OL,13,Fice loss, some of the most rapid and
OL,14,Fconcerning potential processes are now
OL,15,Ffound to be less likely than once
OL,16,Ffeared.
OL,18,FBut ITGC studies have also revealed
OL,19,Fpreviously unknown processes that
OL,20,Fcould weaken the glacier and change
OL,21,Fcurrent projections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
