OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FThe researchers also say that the
OL,7,FThwaites Eastern Ice Shelf (TEIS),
OL,8,Fcurrently covering about half of the
OL,9,F120km-wide front of the glacier, is
OL,10,Flikely to disintegrate in the coming
OL,11,Fdecade.
OL,13,FBut data from the research indicates
OL,14,Fthat Thwaites Glacier has recovered
OL,15,Ffrom past retreat.
OL,17,FRock samples taken by drilling through
OL,18,Fthe ice near the glacier edge show
OL,19,Fthat the glacier was thinner, and the
OL,20,Frocks were at the surface, a few
OL,21,Fthousand years ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
