OL,3,CMuch of Thwaites Glacier could be lost
OL,4,Cby 23rd century, experts say
OL,6,FThe glacier later thickened to cover
OL,7,Fthem, indicating that re-advance and
OL,8,Frecovery of the glacier is possible.
OL,10,FThis raises the future research
OL,11,Fquestion of whether there are any
OL,12,Fmechanisms that might arrest or
OL,13,Fsuspend retreat, and if so, what
OL,14,Fclimate conditions would they need.
OL,16,FOther issues researchers were
OL,17,Fconsidering included how they could
OL,18,Fimprove computer models, and how
OL,19,Fconditions in the area evolved in the
OL,20,Fcoming years.
